{"tid":2251160,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"元朗大廈單位起火 同一時間有人懷疑墮樓","createTime":"2020-10-20T15:01:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T15:23:46.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a48fa67305f329783176a0ca71c25254b17a2967","tid":2251160,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T15:01:36.000Z","msg":"晚上9時許，元朗教育路88號住宅大廈一單位起火，火光熊熊一度冒出濃煙，消防一喉一煙帽到場灌救，亦有多架救護車在場戒備，大批住客疏散至樓下暫避，警方亦封鎖附近一帶道路禁止街坊靠近。火警至10時18分救熄，起火原因仍待調查。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，同一大廈有住客發現有一男子倒卧在二樓平台，懷疑從高處墮下，消防隨即安排雲梯上平台搶救。目前男子傷勢未明，兩宗案件是否有關仍待了解。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201020/RLCBU4JVABARHB5KUV3OQ24GD4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201020%2FRLCBU4JVABARHB5KUV3OQ24GD4%2F&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QWAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=f4078481\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201020%2FRLCBU4JVABARHB5KUV3OQ24GD4%2F&h=98646121\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201020/RLCBU4JVABARHB5KUV3OQ24GD4/</a>"},{"pid":"ded7a8c1304d733f2e545ccff0075c5b7ced0a12","tid":2251160,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T15:03:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\